<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink106">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻi vēṇ ṭaṉṉai yavarnāṭṭut</l>
<l>tutikkā laṉṉan tuṇaicettu mitikkun</l>
<l>taṇkaṭal vaḷaiyiṉu milaṅkumiva</l>
<l>ḷaṅkali ḻākaṅ kaṇṭici ṉiṉaintē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother,</l>
<l>If you look, having thought [about it],</l>
<l>Her pretty, shining body will shine</l>
<l>Even more than the conches</l>
<l>On the cool ocean in his land, </l>
<l>Upon which the goose with quivering legs steps,</l>
<l>Having thought [it was its] mate [lying there?].</l>
</lg>
    </div>
